Choosing Fidelis means aligning your financial life with your faith, values, and community. As Colorados largest Catholic credit union, Fidelis is member-owned, mission-driven, and dedicated to serving the Catholic community.

- Lower fees, higher savings rates, and competitive loan options
- Faith-aligned financial stewardship guided by Catholic values
- Support for Catholic parishes, schools, and charitable causes
- Local and personal service from a trusted team who shares your values

We're excited to partner with you, your family, and your parish!

We currently have 3 locations, with a DTC branch coming this fall!

- Faith-aligned financial stewardship guided by Catholic values

- Local and personal service from a trusted team who shares your values

We currently have 3 locations, with a DTC branch coming this fall!

input_value: Clara Rose Creative (CRC) is a faith-driven design studio dedicated to helping individuals, ministries, and businesses bring their vision to life through purposeful, beautiful branding. Founded by Brittany Sobieski, CRC blends professional design expertise with Catholic values, creating work that is both visually compelling and mission-focused. From custom logos and brand identity packages to marketing materials and event design, CRC serves clients with creativity, integrity, and heartalways striving to reflect truth, beauty, and goodness in every project.
